          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052476/Allard Pierson Museum</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>大型球莖狀的廣口陶土容器或編織容器，用於盛裝水或食物，或用於烹飪，有些附有手把。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052784/TELDAP database (2009-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Huei chachapalmeh tlen patlactic icamac, tlachihualli ica zoquitl tlen moixcatoc, motequihuia para moahcocuiz tlacualli, zo para tlacualchihuazceh, nouhquiya para motlalhuiliz tlamantli.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
